{"tid":81304,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得電腦喇叭好阻地方","createTime":"2017-01-15T08:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T14:49:51.000Z","uid":37458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b52a561a75e9444cbdd242b19e2352fd9317449","tid":81304,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:21:33.000Z","msg":"即係咁<br />\n有時清理電腦枱 既塵<br />\n最煩 個喇叭又多線 好難清<br />\n又阻地方 令到個枱面硬係<br />\n我個mon用臂 <br />\n最近已經開始用airpod配所有裝置<br />\n覺得個喇叭開始無乜用<br />\n係有時兩腦聽歌 可能要用喇叭大聲播歌<br />\n諗緊點解決呢個問題 <br />\n有冇人已經無乜點用大大舊既喇叭"},{"pid":"2798dbc3ec6dd719367b888633ccb7a46ab0c06a","tid":81304,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b080fcee35bd9dc1f7354a92ff52beabad2a947","tid":81304,"uid":60814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:23:44.000Z","msg":"大喇叭先爽皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://holland.pk/42blc3tv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F42blc3tv&h=8f34ee8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5803ba018bcb64976fc8615aaee6b25d958985c1","tid":81304,"uid":39154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:23:46.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"7bdff17a9dd740cd4d5e990a8f885a5b6b4678fe","tid":81304,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:24:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對音質要求唔高<br />\n一般耳筒已經夠我用"},{"pid":"3ef5ce95f63bfaf786a91c10dc54f7f84f34c3a2","tid":81304,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:24:51.000Z","msg":"掛牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b5584e0089683cf0d437a06b3e2e6a06550e19","tid":81304,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"其實大=音質好係一個邏輯謬誤"},{"pid":"008bafa3bebcd79757acbde1e1e19de31b00edce","tid":81304,"uid":45082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:26:50.000Z","msg":"係 所以我轉咗用無線耳筒"},{"pid":"2c483685e630ea5b97cc637cfb3086b55d93082d","tid":81304,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:28:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係 所以我轉咗用無線耳筒</blockquote><br />\n戴耳筒好熱好焗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e9c124fbe6add57e0aa763ede6bba97ab5bf2b","tid":81304,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:33:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實大=音質好係一個邏輯謬誤</blockquote><br />\n大通常係bass靚,同音質的確無乜關係<br />\n但係太細連bass都無,音質再好都無用<br />\n所以係兩樣都要有,唔係得一樣就得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fcd64c152536e66c2e400134d97c671a09ebd33","tid":81304,"uid":52524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:37:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係 所以我轉咗用無線耳筒</blockquote><br />\n戴耳筒好熱好焗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n骨傳導囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113e6323c227150143718a16566eec7f5db82877","tid":81304,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T11:39:39.000Z","msg":"無左喇叭 少好多野<br />\n少堆線 少個火牛"},{"pid":"848a21c5751edcfc2d976bd7362f376ae782aff3","tid":81304,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:08:26.000Z","msg":"用內置喇叭既mon"},{"pid":"83db5675a25076e032e41eed96c0a6af30d12324","tid":81304,"uid":63450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:06:29.000Z","msg":"你間房好細？"},{"pid":"f5717d9ce03be23e37c52d29da37f37d88bb4dfe","tid":81304,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:28:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你間房好細？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係呢個問題<br />\n間房成90尺"},{"pid":"44fb04b12bf4cb280c2fef6e1237cc896d9348f8","tid":81304,"uid":31201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T14:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實大=音質好係一個邏輯謬誤</blockquote><br />\n大通常係bass靚,同音質的確無乜關係<br />\n但係太細連bass都無,音質再好都無用<br />\n所以係兩樣都要有,唔係得一樣就得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大既BASS唔一定靚架喎，睇個發聲元件，有D出BASS好曚好難聽<br />\n當然要有好既SOURCE+DAC+AMP就最好<br />\n線呢D真係有錢就玩冇錢就是Q但<br />\n淘寶舊幾水既SPEAKER都可以係垃圾<br />\n怕阻地方又唔嫌SOUND QUALITY咪買個內置SPEAKER既MOON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c3ad4d9f3d83577bca05b9e1c663c3fd0a5809","tid":81304,"uid":64571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T19:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實大=音質好係一個邏輯謬誤</blockquote><br />\n但係音質好就肯定係有翻咁上下重量/size<br />\n某程度上係你調轉咗理解"},{"pid":"8327518208aa3994c546da0016e576887acb429a","tid":81304,"uid":62947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:54:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實大=音質好係一個邏輯謬誤</blockquote><br />\n但係音質好就肯定係有翻咁上下重量/size<br />\n某程度上係你調轉咗理解</blockquote><br />\n要細喇叭音質好=貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883f9b41c1aa5689241972029f4d6560a556fd76","tid":81304,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:59:14.000Z","msg":"我自己買個喇叭<br />\n數用電腦喇叭<br />\n聲靚好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01480fa392e682cf038701fffb82bf549149147e","tid":81304,"uid":14049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:27:35.000Z","msg":"幾個月前買左兩隻adam a3x +部dac放電腦枱上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30662cc5508047310bff26529dc8e66cfb00b3a5","tid":81304,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:31:36.000Z","msg":"同道中人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又係好中意抹塵<br />\n<br />\nd線啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喇叭，好阻定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef63c778cdf797b027864ce198afa0a6fe23f23","tid":81304,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:32:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同道中人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又係好中意抹塵<br />\n<br />\nd線啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喇叭，好阻定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我換左imac<br />\n<br />\n檯面冇喇叭、聽歌用另一套hi-fi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f86712b64a43892b1c67e69ddbcce023b852d0","tid":81304,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:49:51.000Z","msg":"竟然遇到差唔多嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}